    <h1>Pole Pole: The Swahili Philosophy That Gets Climbers to Uhuru Peak</h1>
    <p>'Slowly slowly' in Swahili. Pole pole is the pacing principle that determines summit success on Mount Kilimanjaro. Why it works, why fast climbers fail, and how to actually do it.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <span>By <a href="/about">Nelson Mushi</a></span>
      <span>&middot; 2026-06-14</span>
      <span>&middot; <a href="/blog">Back to Blog</a></span>
    </div>
  </div>
